---
---

<section id="about" class="relative bg-brand-900 py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-950/40 via-transparent to-brand-950/40"></div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6">
    <div class="mb-2 text-center text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent-500">
      About Us
    </div>
    <h2
      class="text-center font-display text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white md:text-4xl"
    >
      What is GenAI Gurus?
    </h2>

    <div class="mt-10 space-y-8">
      <p class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center text-lg leading-relaxed text-brand-200">
        GenAI Gurus is a global community for builders, researchers, and leaders exploring applied
        Generative AI through practical talks and open discussion. We host expert sessions and
        community conversations focused on real-world GenAI applications, responsible adoption, and
        cross-disciplinary learning.
      </p>

      <div class="grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="group rounded-2xl border border-brand-700/50 bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-800/40 to-brand-800/20 p-6 transition-all hover:border-accent-500/20 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-black/20 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent-500/10 transition group-hover:bg-accent-500/15">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-accent-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.25 6.75 22.5 12l-5.25 5.25m-10.5 0L1.5 12l5.25-5.25m7.5-3-4.5 16.5" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white">Technical depth</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-brand-300">
            Hands-on architecture reviews, model fine-tuning, RAG systems, agent frameworks, and
            production deployment patterns.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="group rounded-2xl border border-brand-700/50 bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-800/40 to-brand-800/20 p-6 transition-all hover:border-accent-500/20 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-black/20 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent-500/10 transition group-hover:bg-accent-500/15">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-accent-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 3v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 6 16.5h2.25M3.75 3h-1.5m1.5 0h16.5m0 0h1.5m-1.5 0v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 18 16.5h-2.25m-7.5 0h7.5m-7.5 0-1 3m8.5-3 1 3m0 0 .5 1.5m-.5-1.5h-9.5m0 0-.5 1.5M9 11.25v1.5M12 9v3.75m3-6v6" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white">Strategic AI leadership</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-brand-300">
            How organizations evaluate, adopt, and scale AI initiatives beyond proof-of-concept
            into real business value.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="group rounded-2xl border border-brand-700/50 bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-800/40 to-brand-800/20 p-6 transition-all hover:border-accent-500/20 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-black/20 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent-500/10 transition group-hover:bg-accent-500/15">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-accent-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 0 1 3.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 0 0 3 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white">Responsible AI</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-brand-300">
            Red-teaming, guardrails, bias mitigation, and governance frameworks that work in
            practice — not just in theory.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center text-lg leading-relaxed text-brand-200">
        GenAI Gurus started in June 2023 as a small Meetup group for people who wanted to go deeper
        than surface-level AI hype. Since then, the community has grown to over 2,000 members and
        50+ events, attracting speakers from leading companies and research institutions.
      </p>

      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl rounded-2xl border border-accent-500/20 bg-accent-500/5 px-8 py-6 text-center">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent-500">Community resource</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-200">
          Preparing for the EU AI Act? We maintain a curated list of official sources, open source tools, templates, and guides.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/eu-ai-act"
          class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-accent-400 transition hover:text-accent-300"
        >
          Explore Awesome EU AI Act
          <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
